    "text": "The logical extension of Sen. Joe Lieberman’s point (“A Holiday for the Rule of Law,” Houses of Worship, May 18) is that by choosing to adhere to the tenets of faith, a society needs fewer secular laws. The measure of a civilized society is how many times and ways people do the right thing without there being a (secular) law that makes them do it.\nJim LeMunyon\n... ",
